Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.81,0:00:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.14,0:00:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pretty good swimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:01:00.83,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an9\bord0\blur0.6\p1\c&H69B7B7&\pos(1282,66)\fscx600\fscy90}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 2,0:00:54.86,0:01:00.83,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\fad(2000,0)\an6\blur0.6\pos(980,108)}Azure Waters
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.41,0:01:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, better get moving.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.48,0:01:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.86,0:01:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the smoke get to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:33.46,0:01:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}His skin is unusually cold...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.43,0:01:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even for someone who's been swimming.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.24,0:01:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.29,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.51,0:01:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.13,0:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. What happened to him?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.01,0:01:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I think it was my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He must have breathed in my cigarette smoke.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.66,0:02:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.82,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly caught a lot again today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.87,0:02:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's get ourselves home.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there something else?{Timing: Generous lead-out. :)}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.84,0:02:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I saw just now, \Nthat boy is quite the swimmer.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.79,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But does he happen to have \Ndifficulty with running?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.01,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if he does?{Interesting article: http://languagelog.ldc.upenn.edu/nll/?p=3483}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.35,0:02:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And is he always very thirsty, \Nperhaps even unusually so?{diabetes.}
Dialogue: 2,0:02:32.63,0:02:39.55,mushishishishishishi,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\bord0\blur1\4c&H41463D&\alpha&HFF&\t(0,3000,1.3,\alpha&H00&)\t(8760,0,0.7,\alpha&HFF&)\fscx130\fscy260\pos(192,164)}Mushi-Shi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:39.55,mushishishishishishi,,0,0,0,,{\shad10\bord1.2\blur0.6\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&H73756E&\alpha&HFF&\t(0,3000,1.3,\alpha&H00&)\t(8760,0,0.7,\alpha&HFF&)\fscx130\fscy260\pos(192,164)}Mushi-Shi
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.14,0:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it that you're getting at?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.86,0:02:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the many strange symptoms {observed and }\Nnoted in mushi-shi records, this boy exhibits several{ of them}:
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.88,0:02:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,low body temperature,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.62,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a delay in speech,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and, the rarest, webbing between the fingers.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.67,0:03:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.37,0:03:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're looking for trouble—
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.61,0:03:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Presuming their cause to be mushi-related, \NI have medicine that can mitigate his symptoms.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.89,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you've noticed that these differences separate your son from other children.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.12,0:03:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It no doubt worries you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's swimming?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even in his sleep?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.57,0:04:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your boy is afflicted with an Uko, or "Rain" mushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.58,0:04:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Separately, each Uko is too tiny to be seen by the naked eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.04,0:04:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But often, they mingle with the rain \Nand flow into rivers.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.68,0:04:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There, they come together \Nand form what resembles a big blue fish...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and flow into the sea to breed.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.11,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Their offspring mingle with water vapor {as it rises}from the sea
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and then fall as{like} rain on mountains and rivers.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.09,0:04:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,They lead a rather simple existence.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.45,0:04:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But on occasion, an Uko may get left behind{ in a deep pool} while the others continue onward,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.97,0:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and to avoid being eaten{ by fish}, it may take up residence in a larger creature, such as a salamander.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.72,0:04:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And in extremely rare cases, \Neven a half-drowned human may become its host.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.39,0:05:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Although the person survives from nearly drowning,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.71,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,they often display symptoms like your son's,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.86,0:05:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and forcibly removing the Uko is impossible.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One can only hope for a flash flood.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.09,0:05:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Uko sometimes leave their hosts{ on their own in an attempt} to try to ride \Nthe flood's turbulent waters and reach the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no telling when that might happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, first things first.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.92,0:05:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him this medicine, and watch over him.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.10,0:06:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times have I told you not to come here at night?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.40,0:06:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You had another dream about water, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.52,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.49,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,My, you caught a big one today, didn't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.40,0:07:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.43,0:07:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do {\i1}you{\i0} want?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.60,0:07:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get lost.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.41,0:07:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that kid's body is as cold as a fish.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.67,0:07:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't be human.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gross...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.79,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.42,0:07:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.37,0:07:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... That thing is huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots. Over there.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play together!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.76,0:07:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.04,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You suck!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.90,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, your body's not really all that cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hear that from, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.95,0:07:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.23,0:08:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.69,0:08:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does the river come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.25,0:08:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from a valley deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does that water{ in the mountain valley} come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes down from the clouds in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where do the clouds in the sky come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.46,0:08:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. They're born from the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where this river goes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.93,0:08:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place with lots and lots of water.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.58,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.37,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've never seen it either...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.41,0:08:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've heard that there's water as far as the eye can see.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.58,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.68,0:08:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sea, the river, the rain, \Nand the clouds are all the same thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They may look different,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're actually all the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.28,0:09:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.27,0:09:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.60,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.49,0:09:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You look well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.55,0:09:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're that old guy {from before }with the smoke.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Old"...{lmao}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.41,0:09:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems you're fine with the smoke now, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.02,0:09:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I guess so.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears that the medicine is working.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.42,0:09:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His body is much warmer now.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.14,0:09:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And before, he used to want nearly \Ntwo whole liters of water every day,{what, that's supposed to be a lot? doctors tell people to drink at least 3 litres a day...}{yeah, seriously. i probably go through more than that myself}{also, i looked this up in the manga because i was curious, and it's 一升 which is an old unit of measurement equating to 1.8 liters. what kind of world was this where drinking 1.8L of water in a day was strange...}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but now, he only wants about seven-tenths as much.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.69,0:10:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.51,0:10:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.93,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have more of the medicine you gave him?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.26,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I must caution you that this is about as much as you can ever hope from it.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.30,0:10:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the mushi is still in him.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.35,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Since Uko do not typically choose humans as hosts,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,it's likely that its ties to him are not that deep.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, in the cases with salamanders,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.27,0:10:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,after only a few years, the hosts become one with the Uko and vanish into the waters.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.84,0:10:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,As you well know, this mushi is rather troublesome.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's going to be okay, isn't he?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.48,0:10:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We should be able to use the medicine to keep his symptoms at bay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.09,0:10:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's enough for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.40,0:10:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can come back again with more of the same medicine.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.77,0:10:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll give you a discount.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.02,0:11:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.42,0:11:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call me that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.70,0:11:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you be back?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.73,0:11:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Early autumn, probably.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.37,0:11:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See you then.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.56,0:11:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't drown anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.48,0:11:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never drowned.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.69,0:11:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have forgotten.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.56,0:11:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you later.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.41,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta? Hurry inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.83,0:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.53,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.38,0:12:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't go to the river!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.53,0:12:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.22,0:12:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginko!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.45,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard there's been a lot of rain here lately.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.97,0:12:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If it keeps raining, there may be a flash flood.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,While it's not without risk,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if we succeed, we may be able to extract the Uko from him.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.23,0:12:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like to try, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.48,0:13:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to be strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.19,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if we manage to do this,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll finally get to be like the other children,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.45,0:13:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and the other villagers will be able to accept you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stay still!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.40,0:13:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not safe.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.02,0:13:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go now.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.41,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.14,0:13:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you go!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.20,0:15:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.61,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.56,0:15:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, please say something.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.82,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.63,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though the rain was so scary before,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.78,0:15:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not scary anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did the Uko leave?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thirsty.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.03,0:15:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.30,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The river's all muddy now,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so let's go to the well near the mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's still thirsty.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is the Uko still in him?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.45,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's burning up.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.16,0:16:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's try to give him some water.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.49,0:16:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.89,0:16:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.74,0:17:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:07.97,0:17:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.18,0:17:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.75,0:17:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.04,0:17:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.42,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does the river come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.38,0:17:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes from a valley deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.13,0:17:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where does that water{ in the mountain valley} come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes down from the clouds in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.65,0:17:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where do the clouds in the sky come from?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.29,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They're born from the sea.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.56,0:17:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.33,0:17:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where this river goes.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place with lots and lots of water.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.45,0:18:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.67,0:18:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He told me earlier that he'd never drowned before.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.82,0:18:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you who drowned in the river, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.38,0:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.89,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened about ten months before he was born.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.12,0:18:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The current is strong today, for some reason.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it rained a lot up in the mountains...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.04,0:19:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I came to, I was on the riverbank.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.34,0:19:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But my husband...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.22,0:19:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His body was found at the bottom of the river.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.61,0:19:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, I found out that I was with his child.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.96,0:19:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt so grateful that our child had been safe within me.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.16,0:19:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more push!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep at it!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.61,0:19:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.09,0:19:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.07,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When he was born, his body was ice-cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.90,0:19:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.28,0:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,he was still alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though everyone was afraid of him,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.61,0:20:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though he may not have been normal,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.01,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,he still managed to live this long.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.77,0:20:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So why? Why did this have to happen now?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Some say...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.57,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,an unborn child, floating within its mother's womb, \Nis closer to a creature of water than to a human.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.09,0:20:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, that may have been why your son became the Uko's host.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.41,0:20:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as he continued growing within your womb,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.54,0:20:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,they became so intertwined \Nthat they became inseparable.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.27,0:20:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... This is all my fault, \Nfor becoming possessed by such a creature.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The day you almost drowned,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.36,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the only reason your son survived was that the Uko happened to save you.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.25,0:21:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, both of you would have died.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.09,0:21:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But he lived.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right here, by your side...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.68,0:21:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,he lived.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.32,0:21:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So the sea, the river, the rain, \Nand the clouds are all the same thing?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.41,0:21:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They may look different,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but they're all actually the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.67,0:21:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuuta, where are you now?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.24,0:21:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you in the river?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.22,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.37,0:21:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.83,0:22:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{These lead with ellipses because they come from an earlier part of the episode.}{i just really don't like how it looks, sorry}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.38,0:22:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not scary anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.06,0:22:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.91,0:22:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're everywhere.
